			Who are SustainiCal users?
		</div>
		<div class="about-detail">
			This competition is intended mainly for UCB students currently living in university housing. Through the year, we hope to assist students in tracking their behavior in order to encourage habits that find valuable. Various student sustainability groups are directly assisting with this project. Several others will be organizing events that we will help you track on this website!
		</div>
		<div class="about-title">
			Why use SustainiCal?
		</div>
		<div class="about-detail">
			We aim to emphasize <b>ease of use, visualizations, and prizes</b>. We are partnering with the UC Berkeley Housing Department to help them achieve their goal of carbon neutrality by 2025. Our main users, students. We hope that an enticing platform and experience will encourage fans to involve their friends into the competition!
